# No environment variables are required for Phase 1 (local vault + transactions) —
# this app is entirely client-side. The variables below are placeholders for
# later phases per docs/finance-tracker-prd.md and are not read by any code yet.

# Phase 3 — AI Planner (stateless /api/ai/plan route, Anthropic API)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Phase 4 — Receipt scanning (stateless /api/ai/receipt route, Claude vision)
# (uses the same ANTHROPIC_API_KEY above)

# Phase 6 — Pro tier cloud backup (Supabase Auth + Storage; encrypted blob only)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
